et/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QwHBlDHxHjNmmwiMhPsXpg">Thu dạ lữ hoài ngâm - 秋夜旅懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADch-bi%E1%BB%87t-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-dW12UVYh-vPxg4IlKpEmEA">Tích biệt hành, tống Lưu bộc xạ phán quan - 惜別行送劉僕射判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADch-du-T%C3%ADch-y%E1%BA%BFt-Hoa-C%C3%A1i-qu%C3%A2n/poem-crS01jzBUNbs6SoUtWJhPg">Tích du (Tích yết Hoa Cái quân) - 昔遊（昔謁華蓋君）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-II/poem-Vy-DL7d5-Nm_0zC_flypBg">Vô đề (II) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-VNhahLxtqyIrLeDASL0s9Q">Thực Hiền</a>)<br></div>	</div>
